Get dataset attributes

get_attrs.Rd

Get dataset attributes in form of named list.

Usage

get_attrs(x)

# S3 method for TealDataset
get_attrs(x)

Arguments

x

an object of (TealDataset) class

Value

named list of object attributes

Examples

# TealDataset --------

library(scda)
ADSL <- synthetic_cdisc_data("latest")$adsl

x1 <- dataset("ADSL", x = ADSL, label = "custom label")
get_attrs(x1)

# CDISCTealDataset --------

library(scda)
ADSL <- synthetic_cdisc_data("latest")$adsl
x3 <- cdisc_dataset(
  "ADSL",
  x = ADSL,
  keys = get_cdisc_keys("ADSL"),
  label = "custom label"
)
get_attrs(x3)
